      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with its distinct individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut and communicative, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed suspension bushings. While displaying honest aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical vitals\u2014specifically the VANOS system and rod bearings\u2014have been proactively serviced. It retains its staggered Style 67 wheels, offering the precise turn-in and neutral handling balance that defines this homologation-bred platform.",
